{"tid":1794863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好灰機，NowTv vs 有線新聞 ，好似用邊個，就另一個好D咁","createTime":"2019-12-23T12:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T07:29:37.000Z","uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9de0129dc04ab7dfcb7eca969f4b3510edc31eb2","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"TLDR懶人包：用NowTv 時就有線好，用有線時就NowTv 好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我之前用老電上網，有NowTV送，呢場運動我用電視睇NowTV，手機apps睇有線，早幾日老電完約，棄NowTV轉有線，原因主要有三：<br />\n<br />\n1.家中藍屍老人家(可能係受廢老fd影響)，對NowTV有偏見，鬧 NowTV「黃媒仆街台」、「誤導你地D後生」、「影到暴徒打人就擰開鏡頭唔影」，但暫未講過有線任何野，唯有轉一轉(我曾經Block左CCTVB 83，無用，佢蠢唔晒，知乜事，死都整返出黎)(所以話咩裝Now/有線救家人，其實未必work，有得救已算萬幸)。<br />\n<br />\n2.手機apps睇有線越來越麻煩，有線新聞台已有D apps睇唔到，有線直播台冇高清(要付費用戶至有)，相反 NowTv不論新聞台定直播台，都仲可以好方便用apps 免費睇仲係高清(呢樣係有線小家)。<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係呢樣</span>，亦係我之前覺得有線做得較好既原因，之前既發夢開花報導：<br />\n<br />\nTLDR2：<span style=\"color: red;\">NowTV直播台幾乎唔出聲冇旁述，有線直播台就比較多旁述。</span><br />\n<br />\nNowTV同有線，都係直播台長影現場，但幾乎唔出聲冇旁述。新聞台有旁述，但唔係長影現場，講一陣冇乜大開花就「現場情況睇到呢度」，要睇現場就轉返直播台；<br />\n<br />\n而有線做得較好既地方就係：當新聞台有旁述，直播台就自動轉去同新聞台聯播，新聞台講完，又自動分家，直播台影返現場：但NowTV就冇咁既安排，新聞台有新聞台講，新聞台講緊同時，直播台依然冇旁述。<br />\n<br />\n***************************************************<br />\n<br />\n好啦，轉電視睇有線，手機apps睇NowTV，點知呢幾日，覺得有線比之前差左，個直播台好似訓左覺！<br />\n<br />\n好似12.21元朗、尖沙咀開花，NowTv直播台同港台32都一早開機直播，有線就後知後覺。今晚「星火不熄」集會，有線又係訓著左，得NowTv直播台有直播，連港台都鳩鳩地流，fb有直播，32台冇。<br />\n<br />\n有冇手足都覺得呢輪有線好似差左少少？"},{"pid":"1ea63cbe853de84e878113be48a0bcdda12c915a","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8875bffa797bc91c14679a9747ee17d5ca9fcc30","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89d6b7a1af0048b6d37cb888c7295d14298becc","tid":1794863,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:54:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6195a7c7161140f38ed0d8c5d69aa8ee627bf9e","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"有線食左屎啊？"},{"pid":"55be0ede3ce6dce9ff94e9a009703e14c5d9f4ba","tid":1794863,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"有線大埔手足果晚一黎就屈搶劫找換店"},{"pid":"13574e2b2dbadbaaae11ac472cbd28bf46eab8a9","tid":1794863,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:22:16.000Z","msg":"有線呢輪喺YouTube大屠殺<br />\n整死我個陳年Channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過直播嚟講最好睇最全面就係蘋果<br />\n立場就器材有限兼冇Youtube<br />\n有線now港台直播都係魚樂無窮mode㗎啦"},{"pid":"cbf3850436bca4bcd37db5fdaf1c39ee0ab5d60a","tid":1794863,"uid":9838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28147b436f5639b607c89527b43096a9666c0648","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf3850436bca4bcd37db5fdaf1c39ee0ab5d60a","tid":1794863,"uid":9838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"講人話電視有用，係覺得佢介面比較難用<br />\n<br />\nTVHK 香港好電視比較易用，可惜已經睇唔到有線新聞台<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tvhkapp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftvhkapp%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=42076129\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tvhkapp/</a>"},{"pid":"8b79ff2169bd35841b6d4e731adf1205818293fc","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有線呢輪喺YouTube大屠殺<br />\n整死我個陳年Channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過直播嚟講最好睇最全面就係蘋果<br />\n立場就器材有限兼冇Youtube<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有線now港台直播都係魚樂無窮mode</span>㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n魚樂無窮mode，形容得好貼切，幾乎係完全唔出聲尤其港台，藍屍老人家就係因為呢個原因，所以唔睇32睇83。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線好在新聞台有旁述就會自動同步。<br />\n<br />\n點解會魚樂無窮mode呢？係咪廣播條例限制左D乜野？"},{"pid":"46630e72837f87eeca786419d9759284e86da3eb","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"所羅門發起白宮聯署要人！<br />\n<br />\n取消北京2022冬季奧運，簽極唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/ask-international-olympics-commission-corporate-sponsors-relocate-or-cancel-beijing-2022-winter-olympics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fask-international-olympics-commission-corporate-sponsors-relocate-or-cancel-beijing-2022-winter-olympics&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=34b55d12\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/ask-international-olympics-commission-corporate-sponsors-relocate-or-cancel-beijing-2022-winter-olympics</a>"},{"pid":"54bd95642ce51eec30962df129bfccfb2442d8a6","tid":1794863,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"如果屋企多廢老，就ＣＡＢＬＥ啦。佢地個有線中蟈組，會爆中蟈日常黑暗史，啱晒廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eccc5f0fe20f570d8eca0b2a7ca010f8dfacc02","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"呢個聖誕黎講，now最多直播，有線最少<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日「和你shop」有線都冇直播，now同RTHK都有<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪要去到有勇武手足裝修、出火魔法，狗出TG之類至會開台？"},{"pid":"6ab582861f050b1932abb7466e0fb34a4c1b50b1","tid":1794863,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"光復上水/上水和你shop，.now 同RTHK都開工，有線又訓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e559aa461c2cefdc567233cd073083f1b3d0632","tid":1794863,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"所以話藍屍冇撚得救<br />\n佢地唔係要真相<br />\n佢地只係要佢地想要既效果"}]}